df_numerize = df

for col_name in df_numerize.columns:
    if(df_numerize[col_name].dtype== 'object'):
        df_numerize[col_name] = df_numerize[col_name].astype('category')
        df_numerize[col_name] = df_numerize[col_name].cat.codes
